[[File:gesture_raised_fist_with_thumb_and_pinky_lifted.jpg|thumb]]'''沙卡手勢'''（[[英語|英語]]：Shaka sign，又稱'''恰卡手勢'''），一個源於[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]互相打招呼示好的手勢<ref name="Watanabe">{{cite web|last=Watanabe|first=June|title=Wherever it came from, shaka sign part of Hawaii|url=http://archives.starbulletin.com/2002/03/31/news/kokualine.html|publisher=Honolulu Star-Bulletin|accessdate=13 January 2011|date=31 March 2002|archive-date=2011-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110810180308/http://archives.starbulletin.com/2002/03/31/news/kokualine.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，做法就是把手的小指和大拇指打出，其餘的手指收起來。沙卡手勢可以表達「你好」、「再見」、「祝你好運」等意思。手勢亦在[[衝浪|衝浪文化]]與[[南美|南美]]流行。<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://caminbrazilandbolivia.blogspot.com/2010/09/brazil-and-i-celebrate-our-two-month.html |title=Cam in South America: Brazil and I celebrate our two-month anniversary: reflections on our relationship |publisher=Caminbrazilandbolivia.blogspot.com |date=2010-09-27 |accessdate=2013-08-20 |archive-date=2012-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120330131815/http://caminbrazilandbolivia.blogspot.com/2010/09/brazil-and-i-celebrate-our-two-month.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==SMS語言==
在[[SMS語言|SMS語言]]裡，沙卡手勢可以有三種表達方式：「\.../」、「\, /」以及「\m/」。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pleiade.org/col_geal/aux_armes-mottoes.html#shaka-sign |title=Aux armes · mottoes: clarere audere gaudere & ζητεῖν τὴν ἀλήθειαν |publisher=Pleiade.org |date=2006-10-01 |accessdate=2013-08-20 |archive-date=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106045917/http://www.pleiade.org/col_geal/aux_armes-mottoes.html#shaka-sign |dead-url=no }}</ref>

